column4: NSLOCTEXT("[E23C1CC14E58AC0F67D0D999E57F34BF]", "03D6BD0F4A592AD18F0271B79180124B", "I\'m MetalMamemon, unbeaten in ninety nine battles! You will be one hundred!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E23C1CC14E58AC0F67D0D999E57F34BF]", "DAAED5A54F6D9B76C9BAD6AB0106EF86", "I don\'t believe anyone like {Player} would run away.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E23C1CC14E58AC0F67D0D999E57F34BF]", "2CC2D04F4632C7455034CDAB1CC27E73", "I knew you would chicken out. Well, let\'s meet when you get more guts.")
